<L>__{interior reception area late afternoon}
<A>__{forsythe comes out to the reception area from an examination room, checks out the patient list, and beckons to mr. parkins.}
<C>__{forsythe}
<D>__{i'm ready for you now, brad.}
<A>__{parkins gets up and follows forsythe into one of the examination rooms.}
<L>__{interior examination room late afternoon}
